# One Dark Matte Syntax theme
A One Dark theme syntax adjusted for matte displays.

Well-chosen colors and contrast gives your eyes comfortable feeling without lost of code focus and readability.

#### JS, JSON, PHP and XML
![A syntax prewiew for JS, JSON, PHP and XML](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/21260478/18004504/a2674a1e-6b94-11e6-8513-3e59b7133081.gif)
